---
title: Presence — MQTT multiplayer flow
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Cam as Camera local
    participant Pres as presence.mjs
    participant Bro as broker.emqx.io
    participant Peer as Remote peer Bob
    participant Scene as THREE.Scene

    Pres->>Bro: connect WSS clientId acg_Alice_xxx
    Bro-->>Pres: connack
    Pres->>Bro: SUBSCRIBE acg/world/world.acg/players/+

    loop every 200ms 5Hz
        Cam->>Pres: position xyz
        Pres->>Bro: PUBLISH players/Alice name xyz t
    end

    Bro-->>Pres: PUBLISH players/Bob name xyz t
    Pres->>Pres: handleRemote data
    alt new peer
        Pres->>Scene: add aura Mesh and label Sprite
        Pres->>Pres: remotes.set name aura label target lastSeen
    else known peer
        Pres->>Pres: target updated lastSeen now
    end

    loop every frame
        Pres->>Scene: aura position lerp target 0.18
        Pres->>Scene: label follows aura plus 1.4y
        Note over Pres: age over 10s fade<br/>age over 30s remove and dispose
    end
